Men's Health Network (MHN) is a non-profit educational organization of health care professionals and interested individuals that focuses on improving male health and wellness.
Menâ€™s Health Network has a Board of Advisors totaling over 800 physicians and other experts from around the world, including Dr. Robert Tan, Dr. Peter Rumm, Dr. S. J. Giorgianni, Dr. Ken Goldberg, Dr. James Sniechowski, and Dr. Judith Sherven. MHN is based in the United States and is incorporated in the District of Columbia.


